description.excerpt:
Skipgram models using TensorFlow, TensorFlow Text and Annoy. This repository/future package bases of negative sampling Skipgram's way of learning to define models able to learn word or item representation. 
This project aims to propose several ways to learn word representation:
Skipgram models for text and recommendation with TensorFlow
